attributes.description: Manic Street Walkers (MSW) is a walk for pleasure club launched in December 31, 2011. It promotes regular walking with a group for the purpose of seeing, discovering, understanding and enjoying the city of Surabaya.
attributes.title: Manic Street Walkers

attributes.description: Strenkali Jagir Wonokromo ternyata memiliki begitu banyak sejarah dan cerita menarik: ada pemukiman banyak pekerja informal, warga-warga yang tinggal pinggir kali dengan kemampuan luar biasa mengelola lingkungannya, desain rumah panggung yang menarik, dan Pak Erik dengan Bali 9 nine yang menjual masakan rica-rica.
attributes.title: Strenkali Jagir, Wonokromo

attributes.description: Established in mid-2008, C2O Library & Collabtive is an independent public library and collaborative creative space located in the heart of Surabaya.
attributes.title: C2O Library & Collabtive
C2O Library & Collabtive to Strenkali Jagir, Wonokromo
